{"tid":445833,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"窮學生儲錢大法","createTime":"2017-10-23T17:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T00:26:24.000Z","uid":152224,"like":19,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8d1758a00fb5aa165a9377bbd31b5486fa22c1","tid":445833,"uid":152224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:35:58.000Z","msg":"個人儲錢方法如下:(月入六千，儲五千)<br />\n<br />\n唔煙唔酒唔蒲(間唔中賭下波,買六合彩)<br />\n唔去旅行(除咗家庭旅行)<br />\n唔睇戲(等多一排網上有得睇)<br />\n4個月剪一次頭髮(勁長先剪)<br />\n淘寶買衫褲(我唔care牌子)<br />\n<br />\n唔上莊,唔住hall<br />\n唔買reference book(網上大把)<br />\n走lecture堂(慳車費,lunch喺屋企食)<br />\n<br />\n唔食早餐(瞓到下午)<br />\nlunch帶飯/食m記/20蚊頹飯<br />\n晚飯返屋企食<br />\n<br />\n唔拍拖(慳最多)"},{"pid":"0f1db93cf2a0258626717ee4c6910542ec0157a3","tid":445833,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a752ba3921085e73b2a435c1e4b8add16ee0dff","tid":445833,"uid":11258,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:38:08.000Z","msg":"大學五件事入面只揀讀書<br />\n你就會儲到錢"},{"pid":"869f4f861a11577d20adad2c7341cca1f9e03ffe","tid":445833,"uid":53378,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:39:10.000Z","msg":"好心讀書時期無家庭壓力<br />\n就唔好死慳死抵儲個雞碎少少錢<br />\n浪費青春"},{"pid":"0042f25878bfb7d4d03878048ef83ea735609667","tid":445833,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"返parttime啦"},{"pid":"4299333a3d46a8439016435398382987543badc1","tid":445833,"uid":101571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-23T17:42:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好心讀書時期無家庭壓力<br />\n就唔好死慳死抵儲個雞碎少少錢<br />\n浪費青春</blockquote><br />\n啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解要樓主可啱可以講下儲返黎啲錢嘅用途"},{"pid":"1d37d5228270682425d898dd58452a00fbb05cd